## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of online resources and the potential bias of sources. Some sources may present a Eurocentric perspective, overlooking the global implications of the Reformation. Additionally, the lack of primary sources from the 16th century may affect the depth of historical analysis. Further research could include a broader range of academic journals and historical documents to provide a more comprehensive understanding of the Reformation's impact.